<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>错误</title>
</head>
<body>
    <hgroup>
        <h1>错误。</h1>
        <h2>处理你的请求时出错。</h2>
    </hgroup>
    <div class="alert alert-error">
        <h4>
            Exception:
        </h4>
        <br />
        <p>
            There was a <b>@Model.Exception.GetType().Name</b> while rendering <b>@Model.ControllerName</b>'s <b>@Model.ActionName</b> action.
        </p>
        <p>
            @Model.Exception.Message
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="alert">
        <h4>
            Stack trace:
        </h4>
        <br />
        <pre>@Model.Exception.StackTrace</pre>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
